Package: wildcatr
Type: Package
Title: Retrieve Data From Sensing Clues Platform
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Melanie", "Arp", , "melanie.arp@sensingclues.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Hugo", "Koopmans", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Functions to retrieve data that you have access to on the Sensing 
    Clues platform. This is the most important building block of the Wildlife 
    Conservation Analytical Toolbox (WildCAT), it allows you to inspect and 
    perform further analysis on your data. The different data types which are 
    available through the Sensing Clues platform are observations, tracks, map 
    layers and ontologies.
